  "texts": [
    "Formally, for a task T and a set of task-specific examples {(xi, yi)}, prompt tuning aims to optimize the following:",
    "This objective function maximizes the likelihood of the correct outputs yi given the inputs xi concatenated with the optimal prompt p *.",
    "Unlike prefix tuning, prompt tuning does not modify the internal workings of the model but rather influences its outputs through carefully crafted input sequences.",
    "Consider a downstream task that utilizes a pretrained LLM denoted as M.",
    "Let the training dataset be represented as D = {(xi, yi)} N i=1, where each training example (xi, yi) consists of an input text xi and its associated true label yi."
